author: USA TODAY, Sara M Moniuszko and Kim Hjelmgaard, USA TODAY
title: Prince Charles tests positive for coronavirus, has 'mild symptoms' but 'remains in good health'
description: Prince Charles is the latest public figure to test positive for the coronavirus. Britain's royal, 71, tested positive after displaying mild symptoms.
